Description: Unique numeric identifier used by CollectiveAccess internally to identify this object checkout entry
UUID for group checkout is part of
The id of the object that was checked out
The user who checked out the object
Date/time the checkout entry was created
Date/time the item was checked out
Date/time the item is due to be returned
Date/time the item was returned
Notes at return of object
Notes made at checkout time
Number of overdue checkouts
User list for all overdue checkouts
Number of checked out items
User list for all items checked out
Number of checked in items
Number of reservations
User list for all reservations
Date/time a coming due notice was last sent
Date/time an overdue notice was last sent
Date/time a reservation available notice was last sent
Indicates if the order is deleted or not
